OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,FVoters in Scotland will elect 129
OL,7,FMembers of the Scottish Parliament,
OL,8,Fwhich will determine who will become
OL,9,Ffirst minister.
OL,11,FUnder the Scottish Parliament's
OL,12,Felectoral system, 73 constituency
OL,13,Frepresentatives will be elected and a
OL,14,Ffurther 56 MSPs will be chosen via
OL,15,Feight regional lists.
OL,17,FFour constituencies are up for grabs
OL,18,Fin Dumfries and Galloway and the
OL,19,FScottish Borders, with additional MSPs
OL,20,Felected via the list system.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
