OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,FCounting is taking place in Dumfries
OL,7,Fand Kelso where results from the
OL,8,Fregion will be announced.
OL,10,FAs polls closed at 10pm on Thursday,
OL,11,Fleaders of the political parties
OL,12,Fthanked their campaigners for their
OL,13,Fwork over the past six weeks.
OL,15,FSNP leader John Swinney said: "Our
OL,16,Fcampaign focused entirely on the
OL,17,Fpriorities of the people of Scotland -
OL,18,Fimproving the NHS, supporting people
OL,19,Fwith the cost of living and delivering
OL,20,Fthe fresh start of independence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778501469
OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,F"And that is exactly how we will
OL,7,Fgovern, if that is the choice that the
OL,8,Fpeople of Scotland have made."
OL,10,FScottish Labour's deputy leader Jackie
OL,11,FBaillie said: "We ran an ambitious
OL,12,Fcampaign and we are proud of it.
OL,14,F"We have championed a serious plan and
OL,15,Fhave put forward a serious and
OL,16,Fcredible candidate for first minister,
OL,17,FAnas Sarwar."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
