OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,7,FFindlay said: "As the polls close, I
OL,8,Fwant to thank all the Scottish
OL,9,FConservative candidates, activists and
OL,10,Fvolunteers who have worked tirelessly
OL,11,Facross Scotland to get our message out
OL,12,Fover this campaign.
OL,14,F"I am proud of our manifesto we
OL,15,Fproduced which was full of ambitious
OL,16,Fpolicies to get Scotland working again
OL,17,Fafter two decades of SNP failure."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
