OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,FScottish Green co-leader Gillian
OL,7,FMackay said: "The Scottish Greens are
OL,8,Fgrateful to everyone who has put their
OL,9,Ftrust in us and backed our positive
OL,10,Fand hopeful vision for Scotland.
OL,12,F"We are also grateful to everyone who
OL,13,Fhas made this election possible,
OL,14,Fincluding everyone who will be working
OL,15,Fand volunteering at the counts."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
