OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,FScottish Liberal Democrat leader Alex
OL,7,FCole-Hamilton said: "As polls close I
OL,8,Fwould like to thank all of the
OL,9,FScottish Liberal Democrat candidates
OL,10,Fand activists who have worked so hard
OL,11,Fto deliver a positive and energetic
OL,12,Fcampaign from the Borders to the
OL,13,FHighlands and Islands."
OL,15,FMalcolm Offord, Reform UK's Scottish
OL,16,Fleader, previously said a vote for
OL,17,FReform UK was "an opportunity for real
OL,18,Fchange and real prosperity to make
OL,19,FScotland the most successful part of
OL,20,Fthe UK."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
