OL,3,CVote counting due to begin in Scottish
OL,4,CParliament election
OL,6,FAfter the polls closed the party
OL,7,Fthanked voters and its campaign teams
OL,8,Fup and down the country.
OL,10,FUnder the Scottish Parliament's
OL,11,Felectoral system, voters elect 73
OL,12,Fconstituency representatives and a
OL,13,Ffurther 56 MSPs via eight regional
OL,14,Flists.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/8
